      "content": "that's a pretty bleak outlook for anyone trying to build something from the ground up. it feels like these policies are basically designed without even thinking about the people running the towns. isn't there a way to look at it where raising the wage actually helps stabilize the workforce and reduces turnover costs for a small business?",
